cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with improving search recall across all eBay classifieds platforms using a supervised model for dominant category prediction. This involves transforming queries to numeric vectors and applying a fully-connected deep convolutional neural network (CNN) for classification. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IR (Information Retrieval), followed by cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, since the paper deals with image classification and natural language processing, it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) sub-categories.
